@startuml quarterly-config-workflow
title Fund Metrics API — Quarterly Config Update Workflow

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Global skin
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
skinparam backgroundColor #F8F9FA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor              #2C5F8A
  LifeLineBorderColor     #AACCE0
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EBF4FB

  ParticipantBorderColor     #2C5F8A
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #D6EAF8
  ParticipantFontColor       #1A3A5C
  ParticipantFontStyle       Bold

  ActorBorderColor     #1A6B3A
  ActorBackgroundColor #D5F5E3
  ActorFontColor       #1A3A1A
  ActorFontStyle       Bold

  NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  NoteBorderColor     #F9A825
  NoteFontColor       #5D4037
  NoteFontSize        12

  DividerBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  DividerBorderColor     #90CAF9
  DividerFontColor       #1565C0
  DividerFontStyle       Bold
  DividerFontSize        13

  GroupBorderColor     #7B1FA2
  GroupFontColor       #7B1FA2
  GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F9F0FF
}

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Participants
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
actor  "Fund Manager"  as FM    #D5F5E3
actor  "Developer"     as DEV   #D6EAF8
actor  "Tester"        as TEST  #FCE4EC

participant "Git / GitHub\n(master)" as GIT   #E8DAEF
participant "CloudBees\n(CI)"        as CB    #FDEBD0
participant "Spinnaker\n(CD)"        as SP    #FDEBD0

box "Environments" #F0FFF4
  participant "SYST" as SYST #C8E6C9
  participant "UAT"  as UAT  #A5D6A7
  participant "Prod" as PROD #66BB6A
end box

participant "ServiceNow\n(SNOW)" as SNOW #F5F5F5
participant "Midnight\nScheduler"  as SCH  #E3F2FD

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 1 — Request
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 1 · Request ==

FM  ->  DEV : Quarterly update request\n<i>New return figures + activation date (e.g. 2025-07-01)</i>

DEV ->  DEV : Create feature branch\n<font color="#2C5F8A">git checkout -b feature/fund-metrics-q3-2025</font>

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 2 — Development
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 2 · Development ==

DEV ->  DEV : Add <b>funds-config-v3.json</b>\nSet version, effectiveFrom, returns

note right of DEV #FFFDE7
  <b>Fields to update in the new file:</b>
  • version        → "3.0.0"
  • effectiveFrom  → "2025-07-01"
  • publishedAt    → today's timestamp
  • performanceAsOf→ last day of prev quarter
  • funds[*].returns → new figures from FM
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  <b>Do NOT modify or delete existing files.</b>
  They form the audit history.
end note

DEV ->  DEV : Verify locally
DEV ->  DEV : <font color="#2C5F8A">./mvnw test</font>\n<font color="#2C5F8A">curl /api/v1/funds/history</font>\n<font color="#2C5F8A">curl /api/v1/funds/preview?date=2025-07-01</font>\n<font color="#2C5F8A">curl /api/v1/funds/chooser</font> → new figures in chooser response?

DEV ->  GIT : Push branch

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 3 — Pull Request
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 3 · Pull Request ==

DEV ->  GIT : Open Pull Request\n<i>Include FM sign-off on figures in description</i>
GIT ->  DEV : Peer review & approval
DEV ->  GIT : Merge to <b>master</b>

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 4 — CI Build
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 4 · CI Build (CloudBees) ==

GIT ->  CB : Merge triggers build
CB  ->  CB : <font color="#2C5F8A">./mvnw package</font> + run all tests
CB  ->  SP : Publish build artefact\n+ create Spinnaker task

note over CB, SP #FFFDE7
  The new config file is embedded in the JAR.
  Tests confirm the new version loads and the
  effectiveFrom date resolves correctly.
end note

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 5 — SYST
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 5 · Deploy & Verify — SYST ==

DEV  ->  SP   : Trigger SYST pipeline
SP   ->  SYST : Rolling deploy (zero downtime)

DEV  ->  SYST : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds/history</font>\n→ v3 present?
DEV  ->  SYST : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds/preview?date=2025-07-01</font>\n→ figures correct?
DEV  ->  SYST : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds</font>\n→ still serving previous version?
DEV  ->  SYST : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds/chooser</font>\n→ fee, return, timeframe, risk all correct?

note right of SYST #D5F5E3
  All four checks must pass
  before promoting to UAT.
end note

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 6 — UAT
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 6 · Deploy & Test — UAT ==

DEV  ->  SP  : Trigger UAT pipeline
SP   ->  UAT : Rolling deploy (zero downtime)

DEV  ->  TEST : Notify — UAT ready for testing
TEST ->  UAT  : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds/preview?date=2025-07-01</font>
TEST ->  FM   : Confirm return figures match sign-off
FM   ->  TEST : Approved
TEST ->  DEV  : UAT sign-off

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 7 — Change Request
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 7 · Change Request (ServiceNow) ==

DEV  ->  SNOW : Raise Change Request\n<i>Build ref · effectiveFrom date · UAT sign-off</i>
SNOW ->  DEV  : CR approved

note over SNOW #FFFDE7
  The CR covers the Prod <b>deployment</b> only.
  The data goes live at midnight on effectiveFrom.
  No second CR is needed for the automatic activation.
end note

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 8 — Prod Deploy
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 8 · Deploy — Prod ==

DEV  ->  SP   : Trigger Prod pipeline
SP   ->  PROD : Rolling deploy (zero downtime)

DEV  ->  PROD : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds/history</font> → v3 present?
DEV  ->  PROD : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds</font> → still serving v2?
DEV  ->  PROD : <font color="#2C5F8A">GET /api/v1/funds/chooser</font> → still showing previous figures?

note right of PROD #FFFDE7
  New config is embedded and ready.
  No user-facing change yet —
  effectiveFrom date has not arrived.
end note

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  Phase 9 — Automatic Activation
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
== Phase 9 · Automatic Activation (no manual step) ==

SCH  ->  PROD : Midnight on 2025-07-01\nScheduler fires <b>refreshActiveConfig()</b>
PROD ->  PROD : v3 becomes active

note over SCH, PROD #D5F5E3
  <b>No deployment. No manual intervention. No on-call required.</b>
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Full config endpoint (ETag/304 caching):
    Micro frontend sends:  GET /api/v1/funds  If-None-Match: "2.0.0"
    API responds:          200  ETag: "3.0.0"  [new fund data]
    Subsequent calls:      304 Not Modified  (until next quarterly update)
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Chooser endpoint (always 200, BFF shaped for fund selection page):
    Micro frontend sends:  GET /api/v1/funds/chooser
    API responds:          200  [new fee, return, timeframe, risk data]
    Both endpoints switch simultaneously — same active config source.
end note

@enduml
